sources.title: Riders of the Desert (1932) BOB STEELE
sources.description:
Stars: Bob Steele, Gertrude Messinger, Al St. John, George "Gabby" Hayes
Director: Robert N. Bradbury

The Rangers in New Mexico are being disbanded but Bob Houston gets them to make one more ride to go after the outlaw gang led by Hashknife.

metadata.Plot: The Rangers in Arizona are being disbanded but Bob Houston gets them to make one more ride. They go after the outlaw gang led by Hashknife. They catch Hashknife, but he escapes taking Barbara with him and Bob and Slim have to go after him again.
metadata.Actors: Bob Steele, Gertrude Messinger, Al St. John
